OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms told to stop 'text   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpests' hassling customers  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Businesses have been warned to act if  
OL,6, their employees use customers' contact 
OL,7, details to send inappropriate messages.
OL,9,FAlmost a third of young people have    
OL,10,Freceived unwanted contact after giving 
OL,11,Fpersonal information to a business, the
OL,12,FInformation Commissioner's Office (ICO)
OL,13,Fsays.                                  
OL,15,FIt said it would remind companies of   
OL,16,Ftheir legal responsibilities when it   
OL,17,Fcame to "text pests" within their firm.
OL,19,FIt has urged those subjected to the    
OL,20,Fpractice to share their experiences.   
